                As people get ready to celebrate Super Bowl Sunday the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration has some sobering numbers for those who donrsquot make the proper travel plans after the parties
                                          







        
    



                                                                                                                                    
                According to the NTSB 40 percent of all traffic fatalities on Super Bowl Sunday are alcohol related AAA MidAtlantic said party planners and football fans should prepare for the festivities by designating a sober driver or arranging for alternate transportation options
                                                                                                                                    
                quotDrinking and driving is not a game Itrsquos a deadly combination and a crimerdquo said John B Townsend II manager of public and government affairs for AAA MidAtlantic ldquoCall the right play and designate a safe and sober driver before you start your celebration Donrsquot fumble when it comes to safetyrdquo
                                          







        
    



                                                                                                                                    
                AAA MidAtlantic also offers some tips to those who attend parties and those who host the event
                                                                                                                                    
                Be a responsible partygoer
                                          







        
    



                                                                                                                                    
                
    If you plan to drive donrsquot drink
    If you plan to drink select a designated driver and give them your car keys If you donrsquot have a designated driver ask a sober friend for a ride home call a cab or stay where you are and sleep it off until you are sober
    Buckle up because itrsquos your best defense against other impaired drivers

                                                                                                                                    
                Be a responsible host
                                          







        
    



                                                                                                                                    
                
    Offer food and nonalcoholic beverages
    Make sure all of your guests designate their sober drivers in advance or help arrange ridesharing with other sober drivers
